Flag Effect <code>enable_checks</code> Enables runtime dimension checks on operations. Recommended during development, disable for release builds once you are confident in your matrix sizes. <code>enable_trace</code> Enables structured tracing via <code>topohedral-tracing</code>. <pre><code>[dependencies]
topohedral-linalg = { version = "3.0", features = ["enable_checks"] }
</code></pre>
